org.gradoop.common.model.api.strategies

Interface PropertyValueStrategy<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The property value type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFixSizedPropertyValueStrategy, AbstractVariableSizedPropertyValueStrategy, BigDecimalStrategy, BooleanStrategy, DateStrategy, DateTimeStrategy, DoubleStrategy, FloatStrategy, GradoopIdStrategy, IntegerStrategy, ListStrategy, LongStrategy, MapStrategy, NullStrategy, SetStrategy, ShortStrategy, StringStrategy, TimeStrategy

    public interface PropertyValueStrategy<T>
    Interface defining the methods necessary to handle the (de-) serialization of a PropertyValue's value.
